snippet.title: Colton Haynes & Amber Heard | Crazy Kids [+ Gerda]
snippet.description:
♥ ♥ ♥ #CAMBER ♥ ♥ ♥

• [HD; 720p] FOR THE BEST QUALITY

• Twitter: https://twitter.com/itsCassyBiatch

• Voiceovers:
Colton: Hey guy´s it´s Colton Haynes
Colton: Eating... it´s a talent... it´s my best talent!
Amber: Hi, its Amber Heard
Amber: My dad actualy try to give me a guun... I got you a pretty one
Colton: I will always love you... That was acting!!!

Gerdas did: Amber Heard
I did: Colton Haynes

• Notes: Ok we are really the Crazy Kids xD I mean 3 collabs in just one week... just wow xD Ok it was a idear that we have today when we talked about my love Colton and her love Amber and than we found pictures from them together and where like ok lets make an video of them... so here it is xD Hope you guys like it and maybe a few from you will also become part of the #Camber train (Colton + Amber = Camber) haha :D
Anyway her parts are real better than mine but its ok as long we have fun by making it :3
